            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">Webflow AI</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#84CC16] text-white px-4 py-2 font-black text-lg">9.1/10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 font-bold">Custom content portfolio with writing samples, client work, and case studies. Full design control for creative agencies.</p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">‚úì PERFECT FOR:</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Agencies with strong portfolio needs</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Custom writing sample showcase</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Case study workflows required</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Want unique brand identity</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Need fast PageSpeed (95+)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Have design resources</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-red-700 mb-3">‚úó AVOID IF:</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Want fast setup (requires 2-3 days)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ No design/development skills</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Simple service page enough</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Budget under $18/month</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Don't need customization</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-lime-50 p-4 mb-4">
            <p class="font-black text-lime-900 text-sm">REAL PERFORMANCE: ContentCraft Agency built Webflow site with scrollable writing samples on homepage, filterable portfolio (SaaS, Fintech, Healthcare), service pages with specific deliverables. Build time: 3 days. Month 1: 67 RFPs (up from 14), conversion rate 31% (up from 7%), revenue $147,000/month (up from $42,000). Samples click-through 623% increase. PageSpeed 97 (mobile), 99 (desktop).</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Custom Portfolio Pages</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Content CMS</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Fast PageSpeed (95+)</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Export Capability</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">$18-42/month</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Squarespace -->
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">Squarespace AI</h3>
            <span class="bg-gray-800 text-white px-4 py-2 font-black text-lg">8.7/10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 font-bold">Professional templates that showcase content quality with integrated inquiries. Built for service businesses.</p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">‚úì PERFECT FOR:</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Agencies focused on services</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Want professional templates</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Need integrated blog for samples</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Fast setup (1-2 days)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ SSL included</li>
