                <li>‚Ä¢ Require advanced CMS</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Want full design control</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Complex case study workflows</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Budget under $23/month</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 mb-4">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-sm">REAL PERFORMANCE: StoryBrand Content (5-person agency) built Squarespace site using agency template, added blog portfolio for writing samples, integrated Calendly for strategy calls. Build time: 2 days. Month 1: 28 RFPs (up from 11), conversion rate 24% (up from 9%), revenue $67,000/month (up from $31,000). Template limitations but adequate for service-focused agencies.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Agency Templates</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Content Galleries</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">SSL Included</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">Blog for Samples</span>
            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-3 py-1 font-black text-sm">$23-59/month</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Framer -->
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 md:p-8">
