            <div>
              <h4 class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">‚úì PERFECT FOR:</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Agencies needing site fast (hours)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Modern visual aesthetic priority</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Fast design iterations</li>
